[link: /commands/categories/core.md] ’Ł@4147bee0cfac6b29fd46596a0b8737547bd4a41d14b0bb32a9a64d19c0e9f3f0ŁYTitle: title: def
Path: Signature
Content:
``> def {flags} (def_name) (params) (block)``
’Ł@b80b9c7c216d26cc34ec5d03968be14136dadb46232a2a4e35399a51a212a2d3ŁŃTitle: title: def
Path: Flags
Content:
``--env``
: Keep the environment defined inside the command.
``--wrapped``
: Treat unknown flags and arguments as strings (requires ...rest-like parameter in signature).
’Ł@9e7d7c6ba67531756d9115c46537783ca7ea1a5b940b3c3a83db860a86438ea5ŁčTitle: title: def
Path: Parameters
Content:
``def_name``
: The command name to define.
``params``
: The command parameters, a comma-separated list inside 
[
]
.
``block``
: The body of the command, a list of instructions inside {}.
